item.description: 2. Add Two Numbers 问题描述： You may assume the two numbers do not contain any leading zero, except the number 0 itself. Example 1 2 3 Input: (2 -> 4 -> 3) + (5 -> 6 -> 4) Output: 7 -> 0 -> 8 Explanation: 342 + 465 = 807. 大概是说给定两个链表表示的非负整
